name: FARTGOAT
description: FARTGOAT emerges from the lore of fartcoin, originally launched five months ago but abandoned and forgotten. A dedicated community rediscovered and revived it, driving the token to an all-time high. By fusing the irreverent flatulence humor of fartcoin with the unrivaled prestige of GOAT—two powerful narratives each commanding over \$100 million market caps—FARTGOAT stands alone as a uniquely potent and hilarious memecoin ready to conquer markets and timelines alike.
